modele.occupant

Class Occupant

  • java.lang.Object
    • modele.occupant.Occupant
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Questionnable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ObjetFixe, ObjetMobile

    public abstract class Occupant
extends java.lang.Object
implements Questionnable
    The Occupant class is an abstract class that implements the Questionnable interface and defines common attributes and methods for all occupants in a grid.
